---
title: Middle Eastern Beef Koftas & Cos Salad with Garlic Yoghurt & Mint
description: Spiced to perfection and packed with flavour, these Middle Eastern beef koftas are a feast for the senses! Served with a crisp cos salad, cooling garlic yoghurt, and fresh mint, every bite is a delicious balance of warmth and freshness. A vibrant dish that’s as satisfying as it is simple!

